      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se variabile di i.p.c. per ragione sociale      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * No richieste ad utente                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-fun-snx-ric      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * No funzionamento ciclico                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-fun-snx-cic      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * No funzionamento automatico                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-fun-snx-aut      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione parametri                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "R"                  to   rr-tip-ord             .
           move      1                    to   rr-sel-vet             .
           move      w-ipc-dlp-tdi-rag    to   rr-rag-min             .
           move      w-ipc-dlp-tdi-rag    to   rr-rag-max             .
           move      rr-rag-max           to   w-all-str-alf          .
           move      20                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           perform   all-str-pad-000      thru all-str-pad-999        .
